{"tid":899571,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【水行俠】首輪影評激讚拍得住《雷神奇俠3》　超越《神奇女俠》","createTime":"2018-11-12T14:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T12:12:46.000Z","uid":105567,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"c89660ca5db0a4b5a3b92d0b982a07dbfff2410e","tid":899571,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:04:18.000Z","msg":"DC今年唯一一部超級英雄片《水行俠》年底壓軸登場，電影被視為新風格的試水之作，首輪影評近日流出市面，觀眾一致大讚將會是繼《神奇女俠》後另一DC救世主。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2073216/org/9445d118951c766c9abd707dfbe490b1.jpg/XZ7nyeb1J6VEBJf2ZeVp4YpjFWmXXBajuJTGULiUxlA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2073216%2Forg%2F9445d118951c766c9abd707dfbe490b1.jpg%2FXZ7nyeb1J6VEBJf2ZeVp4YpjFWmXXBajuJTGULiUxlA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8f8de8f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超級英雄電影近年由Marvel獨領風騷，有傳《正義聯盟》的一面倒負評成為最後一根稻草，令走黑暗路線的DC決心改變風格迎合市場，而以新形象出發的首部作品《水行俠》將於12月上映，近日陸續在美國西岸舉行試映會，評價甚至更勝《神奇女俠》。<br />\n<br />\n影評甚至預言《水行俠》的成功會超越《神奇女俠》。（劇照）<br />\n影評甚至預言《水行俠》的成功會超越《神奇女俠》。（劇照）<br />\n<br />\nReddit用戶MaxBorne在網上發表影評，大讚《水行俠》將會超越《神奇女俠》成為DC最受主流觀眾歡迎的作品，強調電影的風格似足《蟻俠2：黃蜂女現身》和《雷神奇俠3：諸神黃昏》，坦言擔心外界會抨擊電影毫無DC特色，甚至明顯想複製Marvel的成功方程式。Twitter都出現不少搶閘影評，當中mick minas形容《水行俠》是水底世界版《星球大戰》，認為由製作水平和叙事手法都達到新高，並提出希望溫子仁未來執導更多DC電影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/257123/%E6%B0%B4%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%A0-%E9%A6%96%E8%BC%AA%E5%BD%B1%E8%A9%95%E6%BF%80%E8%AE%9A%E6%8B%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%BD%8F-%E9%9B%B7%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E4%BF%A03-%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A-%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E5%A5%B3%E4%BF%A0?fbclid=IwAR2JGWoolNkyIz4dnJHTu046enhTcVcOI6MyXOcwZts5VPSyHnYt-E1-Z1s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F257123%2F%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BF%25A0-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25BC%25AA%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E8%25A9%2595%25E6%25BF%2580%25E8%25AE%259A%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%25BE%2597%25E4%25BD%258F-%25E9%259B%25B7%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%25A5%2587%25E4%25BF%25A03-%25E8%25B6%2585%25E8%25B6%258A-%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%25A5%2587%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BF%25A0%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2JGWoolNkyIz4dnJHTu046enhTcVcOI6MyXOcwZts5VPSyHnYt-E1-Z1s&d=zKUfNEAgjCwU09ksVv1QEHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=d9650466\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/257123/%E6%B0%B4%E8%A1%8C%E4%BF%A0-%E9%A6%96%E8%BC%AA%E5%BD%B1%E8%A9%95%E6%BF%80%E8%AE%9A%E6%8B%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%BD%8F-%E9%9B%B7%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E4%BF%A03-%E8%B6%85%E8%B6%8A-%E7%A5%9E%E5%A5%87%E5%A5%B3%E4%BF%A0?fbclid=IwAR2JGWoolNkyIz4dnJHTu046enhTcVcOI6MyXOcwZts5VPSyHnYt-E1-Z1s</a>"},{"pid":"37497e99814290bc15cadbe497be1e02b446d5b5","tid":899571,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T14:05:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2073304/org/241624993270de97858d2e49153767de.jpg/vQ9Q2wet_qNwiEywLbtxZAkVJBBn9zrUzy3Uic8t1Ik\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2073304%2Forg%2F241624993270de97858d2e49153767de.jpg%2FvQ9Q2wet_qNwiEywLbtxZAkVJBBn9zrUzy3Uic8t1Ik&h=036fed08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2073307/org/e9a3fab040a3a05132d0e7394e8c7ecc.jpg/8PKQc2JmyxXedZ-ZEsZQ_S4KozmE2qCxSzMNDUszDQ0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2073307%2Forg%2Fe9a3fab040a3a05132d0e7394e8c7ecc.jpg%2F8PKQc2JmyxXedZ-ZEsZQ_S4KozmE2qCxSzMNDUszDQ0&h=d6483ebe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2073306/org/025de33d2fb38cce3cfc743ca8311c16.jpg/hgXV1yag_XBu-89ETOODlpAqfhGmBGK_9NkZEfTZGRE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2073306%2Forg%2F025de33d2fb38cce3cfc743ca8311c16.jpg%2FhgXV1yag_XBu-89ETOODlpAqfhGmBGK_9NkZEfTZGRE&h=d1d45b4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2073305/org/aa6ef0e4d6106e4edb2b729375ea1795.jpg/RS63ncvBIRlQQ1eB5t5swqifhk2pmxAk